{"id": "art-217", "label": "Art. 217", "title": "Art. 217: Conţinutul cauţiunii", "slug": "art-217", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 217: Con&#355;inutul cau&#355;iunii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1228584118\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2203\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1228584118\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consemnarea cau&#355;iunii se face pe numele\ninculpatului, prin depunerea unei sume de bani determinate la dispozi&#355;ia\norganului judiciar ori prin constituirea unei garan&#355;ii reale, mobiliare\nori imobiliare, în limita unei sume de bani determinate, în favoarea\naceluia&#351;i organ judiciar.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1801889018\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2202\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1801889018\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Valoarea cau&#355;iunii este de cel pu&#355;in 1.000 lei\n&#351;i se determin&#259; în raport cu gravitatea acuza&#355;iei aduse\ninculpatului, situa&#355;ia material&#259; &#351;i obliga&#355;iile legale ale\nacestuia.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_33753261\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2201\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_33753261\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Pe perioada m&#259;surii, inculpatul trebuie s&#259;\nrespecte obliga&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la art. 215 alin. (1) &#351;i i se\npoate impune respectarea uneia ori mai multora dintre obliga&#355;iile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 215 alin. (2). Dispozi&#355;iile art. 215 alin. (3)-(9)\nse aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_78805771\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2200\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_78805771\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Cau&#355;iunea garanteaz&#259; participarea inculpatului\nla procesul penal &#351;i respectarea de c&#259;tre acesta a obliga&#355;iilor\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (3).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1668013205\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2199\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1668013205\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Instan&#355;a de judecat&#259; dispune prin\nhot&#259;râre confiscarea cau&#355;iunii, dac&#259; m&#259;sura controlului\njudiciar pe cau&#355;iune a fost înlocuit&#259; cu m&#259;sura arestului la\ndomiciliu sau a arest&#259;rii preventive, pentru motivele prev&#259;zute la\nalin. (9).</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1610748549\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2198\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1610748549\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În celelalte cazuri, instan&#355;a de judecat&#259;,\nprin hot&#259;râre, dispune restituirea cau&#355;iunii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_143380075\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2197\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_143380075\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (5) &#351;i (6) se aplic&#259;\nîn m&#259;sura în care nu s-a dispus plata din cau&#355;iune, în ordinea\nurm&#259;toare, a desp&#259;gubirilor b&#259;ne&#351;ti acordate pentru\nrepararea pagubelor cauzate de infrac&#355;iune, a cheltuielilor judiciare sau\na amenzii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_96443662\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2196\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_96443662\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)În cazul în care dispune o solu&#355;ie de netrimitere\nîn judecat&#259;, procurorul dispune &#351;i restituirea cau&#355;iunii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_399846329\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2195\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_399846329\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)În cazul în care, pe durata m&#259;surii controlului\njudiciar pe cau&#355;iune, inculpatul încalc&#259;, cu rea-credin&#355;&#259;,\nobliga&#355;iile care îi revin sau exist&#259; suspiciunea rezonabil&#259;\nc&#259; a s&#259;vâr&#351;it cu inten&#355;ie o nou&#259; infrac&#355;iune\npentru care s-a dispus punerea în mi&#351;care a ac&#355;iunii penale împotriva\nsa, judec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i, judec&#259;torul\nde camer&#259; preliminar&#259; sau instan&#355;a de judecat&#259;, la cererea\nmotivat&#259; a procurorului ori din oficiu, poate dispune înlocuirea acestei\nm&#259;suri cu m&#259;sura arestului la domiciliu sau a arest&#259;rii\npreventive, în condi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute de lege.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 5:Arestul la domiciliu</span></b></p>"}